cityOrState:
Neb. State Con
(niece Maggie McLean Bakers
second week of typhoid fever)
fullText:
Lunched with Mrs.
Stanton & her Maggie - Mr
Lawrence ill - & going to California
with his father & mother
summaryText: Lunch with Mrs. Stanton and Maggie, Mr. Lawrence is ill and going to California with his parents.
